pulses.name: 20240828 Most Active Threat Indicators
pulses.description:
28 Aug 2024 : Most Active Threat Indicators
#Cybersecurity #Cyberattack #RCE #Botnet #IOC

Top 3 Source Countries:

- United States (US): Responsible for multiple attacks using various scanners like Censys, ZGrab, and Nmap, as well as SQL injection and botnet activity.
- China (CN): Involved in attacks exploiting vulnerabilities in D-Link devices, Apache HTTP Server, and the Mozi botnet.
- India (IN): Observed in attacks targeting vulnerabilities in GPON routers, NETGEAR devices, and D-Link devices, as well as Mozi botnet activity.
